2005-12-20  Kay Sievers  <kay.sievers@vrfy.org>

	Remove HAL created mountpoints on HAL startup.

	* fdi/policy/10osvendor/20-storage-methods.fdi:
	* tools/Makefile.am:
	* tools/callouts/hal-system-storage-cleanup-mountpoints:

