	* doc/spec/hal-linux26.dia:
	* doc/spec/hal-linux26.png: New files

2004-08-02  David Zeuthen  <david@fubar.dk>

	* doc/spec/Makefile.am (FIGURE_FILES): Remove hal-devices-virtual1.png

