2004-01-04  Joe Shaw  <joe@ximian.com>

	* hald/main.c (PendingUpdate_s): Remove the "const" from the
	"key" field, since it's supposed to be freed.

	* hald/linux/linux_class_block.c: #include <glib.h>.
